modName: succubus race body with support for back equip xpmse and belly grow
summary: conversion body for succubus race to work with xpmse back equip and belly grow slider
descriptionHtml:
Install mesh: data\mesh\actors\Character\succubilite\body
(after run fnis with arm patch fix, maybe not i don't know run always is not bad) 
texture from lb goes in the original spot so don't put them in succubusbody folder, but in default texture actors folder the same in the original file from lb.
body base cbbe tbbp, see required for texture

istall all main file body + skeleton

recommended mod with succubus race is  /\PSQ PlayerSuccubusQuest/\  with transform pack (1.X\2.x\3.x) you can mix them for unique result
required a lot of stuff and reading for working but is perfect for succubus playthrough (pic[url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/156447839@N08/34979496994/in/datetaken-public/]:D[/url] [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/156447839@N08/34979496014/in/datetaken-public/]:D[/url] [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/156447839@N08/35624454132/in/datetaken-public/]:D[/url] [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/156447839@N08/35623225481/in/datetaken-public/]:X[/url] [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/156447839@N08/35623211891/in/datetaken-public/]:X[/url] [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/156447839@N08/34944996503/in/datetaken-public/]:X[/url]) https://www.loverslab.com/files/file/667-psq-playersuccubusquest-for-sexlab/ 

i add a different version of sound trasformation for PSQ 3.2.8a under MISCELLANEOUS
